<!DOCTYPE topic SYSTEM "mingle_help.dtd">
<topic title="Configuring Mingle's authentication">
	
	<p>The authentication settings for Mingle are controlled through the <path>[mingle_data_directory]/config/auth_config.yml</path> file. This file is created by default on all brand new installations.</p>
	
	<section title="Using other authentication systems">
    <p>You can <cref topic="mingle_ldap_authentication">configure Mingle to use LDAP for authentication</cref>.</p>
    <p>You can <cref topic="mingle_cas_sso_authentication">configure Mingle to CAS for authentication</cref>.</p>  
  </section>

